# Optional analytics — GoatCounter
#
# If you want privacy-respecting analytics, sign up at https://goatcounter.com
# and put the resulting endpoint URL here. If unset, no analytics are loaded.
#
# The PUBLIC_ prefix tells Astro this value is safe to expose to the client
# (which it must be, for an analytics script tag).
#
# In GitHub Actions, set this as a repo-level variable (Settings → Secrets and
# variables → Actions → Variables) named PUBLIC_GOATCOUNTER_URL.

PUBLIC_GOATCOUNTER_URL=
